  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿，干员，听好了！这件事很重要，而你是执行它的最佳人选。不过，我注意到其他人也对这笔交易感兴趣……\n我想要这笔交易，但问题是，我现在没法支付那么多钱，目前还有其他事情要处理。不过，我可以支付比别人多得多的报酬。如果你能帮我，我会给你超出你所需的酬劳。怎么样，我们有交易吗？",
    "en": "Hey operator, listen up! This is an important matter, you are the perfect guy for this. But I noticed that the outsider got interested in that deal aswell...\n\nI want it, problem is that I am not able to pay that much right now, got other problems to handle right now. I will pay more than the others so if you can help me out, I can give you way more than you need. Do we have a deal?"
  },
